description: HQDA Elderly Life Network Corp. provides senior housing and retirement products and services in China. The company was formerly known as Hartford Retirement Network Corp. and changed its name to HQDA Elderly Life Network Corp. in June 2018. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Rosemead, California. HQDA Elderly Life Network Corp. is a subsidiary of HQDA International Holdings Ltd.
